move through a creature's space, it takes 10 fire, lightning,
necrotic, psychic, radiant, or thunder damage (you choose
which type), and you can't use this feature to deal damage
to that creature until the start of your next turn.
This effect lasts for 10 minutes. After using this feature,
you must finish a long rest before you can use it again.</description>
